short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds personality types and astrology data next to the names of real people or fictional characters across various platforms.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension shows the personality type (MBTI, Socionics, Enneagram) and the astrological Big 3 (Sun, Moon, Rising) next to the name of real people and/or fictional characters’ as you browse the web. Whether you're on social media, reading articles, or exploring content, you'll instantly see personality and astrology insights of friends, family, celebrities, and fictional characters.

Great for anyone interested in psychology and/or astrology, you can customize what’s shown, save your own typings, and choose to see only your custom list.

Note: The extension is temporarily disabled on YouTube.
